items.name: Anna Miller (Metro) LoRA
items.description:
Anna Miller from Metro series by 4A Games.

Works better with lower CFG vaules (3-6).

Recommended weight range is around 0.4-0.7 depending on the model and CFG vaule. I found that between 0.56-0.6 works decent enough with HiRes fix.

Weight could be reduced when using SD upscale or certain img2img actions.

**Model should know 'wearing a post apocalyptic outfit with beanie' , 'wearing tank top and dog tags' and 'wearing armored tank top and scarf' prompts.

**extra propts might be buggy and don't work properly, will require further improvements.

Example promts; metroannamiller wearing a post apocalyptic outfit with beanie standing in a forest / metroannamiller wearing tank top and dog tags in a train / metroannamiller wearing armored tank top and scarf in a desert like area.

Extra Info:

Dataset for the model was around 31 pictures including in game screenshots and some pictures from the web and manually captioning images.

Released as an alpha, i will try to improve it further on my free time.

Crediting when using this model in merges and such is much appreciated.

Zovya's RPG v3 was used for the pictures.

If you want to support my work, buy me a Coffee!
